data.description: Two acres in a great Lewisville location. Plenty of space for parking with two driveways and a 2-car carport. Garden Space. Owners have made many improvements since the home was purchased in 2017. One-level living with this classic 1960's ranch home. Full basement with great storage and a home gym. Gym equipment can remain. See attached document for long list of improvements made. Mudroom/Pantry is not heated so it is not included in square footage. It was created from the former screened porch between the carport and kitchen.
